snippet.src: (function (win, doc, style, timeout) { var STYLE_ID = 'at-body-style'; function getParent() { return doc.getElementsByTagName('head')[0];} function addStyle(parent, id, def) {if (!parent) { return;} var style = doc.createElement('style'); style.id = id; style.innerHTML = def; parent.appendChild(style);}function removeStyle(parent, id) { if (!parent) { return;} var style = doc.getElementById(id); if (!style) { return;} parent.removeChild(style);} addStyle(getParent(), STYLE_ID, style); setTimeout(function () { removeStyle(getParent(), STYLE_ID);}, timeout);}(window, document, "body {opacity: 0 !important}", 3000))
